com.ipt.ebsa.manage.deploy

Class ApplicationDeployment

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ipt.ebsa.manage.deploy.ApplicationDeployment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Deployment

    public class ApplicationDeployment
extends java.lang.Object
implements Deployment
    Central container class for all of the facts about a deployment. This is also a jump off point for the actual execution. Implements the run() method on the basis that it might execute as a Thread in some way.
